# Stage 1: Dependencies builder
FROM python:3.11-slim AS deps-builder

WORKDIR /app

RUN apt-get update && \
    apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends build-essential \
    && rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

COPY requirements.txt .

RUN pip install --no-cache-dir \
    --extra-index-url https://download.pytorch.org/whl/cpu \
    -r requirements.txt

# Stage 2: Model builder
FROM deps-builder AS model-builder

WORKDIR /app

COPY download_model.py .
RUN python download_model.py

# Stage 3: Runtime
FROM python:3.11-slim AS runtime

WORKDIR /app

RUN useradd --create-home --shell /bin/bash appuser

COPY --from=deps-builder /usr/local/lib/python3.11/site-packages /usr/local/lib/python3.11/site-packages

COPY --from=model-builder /app/model.pt .

COPY --chown=appuser:appuser . .

USER appuser

EXPOSE 8000

LABEL maintainer="team@example.com" \
      description="ML inference service with FastAPI" \
      version="1.0"

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=60s --retries=3 \
    CMD python -c "import urllib.request; urllib.request.urlopen('http://localhost:8000/health')" || exit 1

CMD ["uvicorn", "main:app", "--host", "0.0.0.0", "--port", "8000"]
